<MELItem itemNbr="21-71-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-21-71-01.1.2-21-71-01">
<Title>Flight Deck Humidification System</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="D" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative off provided water supply valve is deactivated closed.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Deactivate the flight deck humidification system water supply valve closed. (AMM DDG 21-71-01).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Set overhead panel (P5) HUMID switch to OFF.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>On AIR DISTRIBUTION EICAS maintenance page 2, confirm flight deck humidifier HUMID S/O VLV indicates CLSD.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open circuit breaker HUMIDIFIER-	FLT DECK and lock with an INOP tag.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>If HUMID S/O VLV did not indicate CLSD in step 2:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to the humidifier shutoff valve.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Turn the manual open/close knob to set the valve in the closed position.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
<MELSubItem itemNbr="21-71-01-01">
<Title>HUMID Switch ON Light (*)</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="D" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELSubItem>
